OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fgradually fade this evening to leave
OL,7,Fclear spells, although the odd
OL,8,Foutbreak of rain is still possible at
OL,9,Ftimes overnight. Winds also easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA spell of persistent rain
OL,12,Fspreads across the region during the
OL,13,Fmorning, followed by sunny spells and
OL,14,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,15,FTurning increasingly windy through the
OL,16,Fday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
