OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWindy
OL,6,Fon Thursday with blustery showers and
OL,7,Fa risk of thunder. Showers less
OL,8,Ffrequent on Friday. A spell of rain
OL,9,Fand stronger winds possibly arriving
OL,10,FSaturday. Fresher than of late.
